      "content": "it just feels like i'm putting in so much effort to stay \"connected\" and it doesn't even matter. honestly, there's a weird part of me that thinks just... letting go... would be so much quieter. like, if i just faded out, there wouldnt be all this pressure to be someone or do something. it sounds peaceful, in a way.",
